From 2b945b2673c977860b50990e5f53d995a9450535 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tianyuan Jiang <code_0002@163.com>
Date: Wed, 22 Jul 2026 06:01:53 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 6/8] dt-bindings: add bindings for Xiaomi Pad 6S Pro
 peripherals

Add bindings for the following peripherals on Xiaomi Pad 6S Pro (sheng):
- giantec,gt9764: camera lens VCM actuator
- ovti,ov02b1b: 2MP depth camera sensor
- ovti,ov32d40: 32MP front camera sensor
- parade,ps5169: USB-C DP alt mode retimer
- nanosic,wn8030-sheng: wireless charging receiver
- novatek,nt36532e + xiaomi,sheng-nt36532e: dual DSI display panel

Signed-off-by: Tianyuan Jiang <code_0002@163.com>
---
