 .../bindings/media/i2c/giantec,gt9764.yaml    | 67 ++++++++++++++++
 .../bindings/media/i2c/ovti,ov02b1b.yaml      | 75 ++++++++++++++++++
 .../bindings/media/i2c/ovti,ov32d40.yaml      | 79 +++++++++++++++++++
